    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so dismissive of anything that isn't a prescription pill and i really just want to give the natural route a shot. i looked up some studies and a lot of people say st johns wort works the same way for mild to moderate cases. if i just take it a few days after my last zoloft dose, is that really gonna be an issue? isn't the herb basically just a milder version of the same thing?",
